---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const officialRegistryZipUrl = 'https://sor.dps.texas.gov/Search/Default/SearchByZipCode';
---

<Layout
  title="Registry Disclaimer | The Princeton Journal"
  description="Legal and source disclaimer for The Princeton Journal registry page."
  url="https://theprincetonjournal.com/registry-disclaimer"
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-10">
    <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-500">Registry Disclaimer</p>
    <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight">Registry Disclaimer</h1>

    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-800">
      <p>
        The Princeton Journal publishes public registry data and state-provided records for public information and
        safety education. The Princeton Journal is not the source of these records and does not create, verify, or
        maintain them.
      </p>

      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-300 bg-gray-50 p-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide text-gray-700">Important Notice</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 list-disc space-y-3 pl-5 text-base leading-7 text-gray-800">
          <li>The Princeton Journal does not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or current status of public registry data shown on this site.</li>
          <li>State-provided records may be updated, corrected, or changed at any time by the registering agency or the Texas Department of Public Safety.</li>
          <li>The official Texas Department of Public Safety registry is the authoritative source and should be used to confirm all details.</li>
          <li>This site must not be used to harass, threaten, intimidate, discriminate against, or otherwise misuse information about any person.</li>
          <li>Registry inclusion is a legal status and public record matter. It is not a statement by The Princeton Journal about any person’s present conduct or current threat level.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Source And Accuracy</h2>
      <p>
        Public registry data shown on this site is reproduced from the Texas Department of Public Safety sex offender
        registry and related state-provided records. Accuracy, availability, and update timing are determined by the
        registering agency and Texas DPS, not by The Princeton Journal.
      </p>

      <p>
        A name, address, status label, photo, or map location on this site should not be treated as independently
        verified by The Princeton Journal. Users should always compare any detail with the official registry before
        relying on it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Responsible Use</h2>
      <p>
        This page is intended for lawful public information and safety education. It is not an instruction, invitation,
        or endorsement to engage in harassment, vigilantism, intimidation, discrimination, doxxing, threats, or any
        unlawful conduct.
      </p>

      <p>
        If a person believes this site displays a mismatched image, a display error, a removal concern, or another
        issue concerning how a public registry record appears on this site, they may contact The Princeton Journal for
        review. Questions about the underlying official registry record should also be directed to Texas DPS or the
        registering agency because those entities control the authoritative source record.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">Official Registry And Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Official registry: <a class="font-semibold underline" href={officialRegistryZipUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Texas Department of Public Safety search by ZIP code</a>
      </p>

      <p>
        Contact for corrections, removal concerns, or other issues about how a public registry record appears on this
        site:
        <a class="font-semibold underline" href="https://collincountyjournal.com/contact/">Contact The Princeton Journal</a>
      </p>

      <p class="text-base text-gray-600">
        This page is an informational notice and not legal advice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
